Class TauStep<T extends Term,A extends Atom,U extends Update>

  • java.lang.Object
    • goal.tools.mc.program.goal.trans.TauStep<T,A,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of term associated with the KRT that the agent to which the step belongs uses.
    A - The type of atom associated with the KRT that the agent to which the step belongs uses.
    U - The type of update associated with the KRT that the agent to which the step belongs uses.
